songs.title: End Is Near

Got problems lookin' at your face, it may be fear
Oh-oh, oh-oh
Got problems lookin' at your face, it may be fear

It may be fear or 'cause I'm weird
Got problems in the darkest place
I may shed tears 'cause hell is near
And I didn't have any time to pack anything today
And I didn't have any time to pack anything today
